{"title":"“突击”任务","authors":["张志民"],"dates":[{"year":1956,"month":12,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"“突击”任务"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张志民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么事忙坏了乡指导员？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"累得他满头冒大汗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半夜里来召集干部会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶起了社长，委员……一大串："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的在瞌睡；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的在揉眼；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的像是惊弓鸟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"混身一直打冷战……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指导员站在油灯前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一边擦汗一边喊："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“干部同志们！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶快回去作‘动员’，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男女老少、整半劳力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连夜起来干！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村边的麦地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通通要浇过一遍水；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路旁的树秧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十步一棵要栽全……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任务十分紧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"完成要在天明前！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人问：“那么多麦地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一会儿怎么能浇透？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人说：“这样儿栽树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活不活可不保险！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指导员脸上流着汗："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“有什么意见以后提，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在讨论没时间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活不活、透不透，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱先别管，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要知道，明天要来参观团！”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}